---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Elysian Development Group | Who Is Abebe?">

  <Header>
    <Fragment slot="title">Elysian Development Group</Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      A public-records review of captured Elysian advisor and project material.
    </Fragment>
  </Header>

  <main class="article-wrap">
    <article class="article-body report-page">

      <p class="lede">
        This report collects Elysian Development Group material captured in the
        archive, including advisor-page references and St. George Crossing project
        material that should be reviewed alongside the Direct Invest record.
      </p>

      <div class="notice-box">
        <strong>Scope:</strong>
        This page is a working research file based on captured public-facing
        web material. It separates captured website evidence from unanswered
        questions about entity records, source dates, and project relationships.
      </div>

      <h2>Elysian Website</h2>

      <a class="document-row" href="https://www.edg.world/" target="_blank">
        <span>Website</span>
        <strong>Elysian Development Group</strong>
        <p>Live public website for Elysian Development Group.</p>
      </a>

      <h2>Advisor Page Capture</h2>

      <p>
        The captured Elysian advisor page shows Mike Abebe and Carlton Brown
        appearing in advisor material. Carlton Brown is also present in the
        archived Direct Invest partner material, making him a bridge between the
        two research threads.
      </p>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/entities/elysian-development-advisors-page.png"
          alt="Elysian Development Group advisors page showing Mike Abebe and Carlton Brown"
        />
        <figcaption>Captured Elysian Development Group advisor page showing Mike Abebe and Carlton Brown.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>St. George Crossing Project Material</h2>

      <p>
        The archive also includes Elysian project-page material associated
        with St. George Crossing in Waynesboro, Georgia. The captured page shows
        the project in a public-facing development context and includes visual
        project material connected to the same Waynesboro development reviewed
        elsewhere on this site.
      </p>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/projects/st-george-crossing-elysian-projects-page.png"
          alt="Elysian project-page capture for St. George Crossing"
        />
        <figcaption>Captured Elysian project-page material associated with St. George Crossing.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Renderings and Project Visuals</h2>

      <p>
        The St. George Crossing source archive includes public-facing renderings
        and site visuals. These images help connect the Elysian project-page
        reference to the larger Waynesboro development file.
      </p>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/projects/st-george-crossing-rendering-main.png"
          alt="St. George Crossing main project rendering"
        />
        <figcaption>Main public-facing rendering associated with St. George Crossing.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/projects/st-george-crossing-entrance-rendering.png"
          alt="St. George Crossing entrance rendering"
        />
        <figcaption>Entrance rendering associated with St. George Crossing project materials.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/projects/st-george-crossing-site-plan.png"
          alt="St. George Crossing site plan"
        />
        <figcaption>Site-plan image associated with St. George Crossing project materials.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Working Notes</h2>

      <div class="fact-grid">
        <div class="fact-card">
          <span>Verified</span>
          <p>
            The archive contains captured Elysian material showing Mike Abebe
            and Carlton Brown in advisor-page context, plus captured St. George
            Crossing project material for Waynesboro, Georgia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fact-card">
          <span>Observation</span>
          <p>
            Carlton Brown appears in both the Direct Invest archived material
            and the Elysian advisor material, making him a recurring name across
            these development records. Elysian material also presents St. George
            Crossing as a project with renderings and project visuals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fact-card">
          <span>Open Question</span>
          <p>
            The exact relationship between Elysian Development Group, Direct Invest,
            St. George Crossing, and related LLCs needs additional source records.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="section-card" href="/reports/direct-invest-group">
        <span>Related Report</span>
        <h3>Direct Invest Group</h3>
        <p>
          Review the source-code and Wayback trail that identified Mike Abebe
          in Direct Invest archived material.
        </p>
      </a>

    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />

</BaseLayout>
